### AboutSL API Tests - Destinations

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api
@contentType = application/json
@authToken = YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### ==========================================
### PUBLIC ENDPOINTS (No Auth Required)
### ==========================================

### 1. Get All Destinations
GET {{baseUrl}}/destinations

### 2. Get Top Rated Destinations
GET {{baseUrl}}/destinations/top?limit=6

### 3. Get Destinations by Category
GET {{baseUrl}}/destinations?category=cultural

### 4. Search Destinations
GET {{baseUrl}}/destinations?search=rock

### 5. Get Single Destination
GET {{baseUrl}}/destinations/DESTINATION_ID_HERE

### ==========================================
### ADMIN ENDPOINTS (Auth Required)
### ==========================================

