### 7. Update Destination
PUT {{baseUrl}}/destinations/DESTINATION_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Sigiriya Rock Fortress - Updated",
  "status": "active"
}

### 8. Toggle Destination Status
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/destinations/DESTINATION_ID_HERE/status
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 9. Delete Destination
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/destinations/DESTINATION_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 10. Get Admin Statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/destinations/admin/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
